A Russian thrill-seeker has taken sofa surfing to a whole new level after a video showed him being dragged along behind his car while sitting in his armchair.

Alexander Shapovalov claimed he had been planning to take the old chair to the rubbish tip but could not fit it into his car.

So the 23-year-old decided on a novel mode of transport instead-  tying the armchair to the back of his car and jumping on it for the ride.

