Russian police are now investigating the video and have warned they are considering bringing charges against him. 

The video, shot by Shapovalov and his friends, show the adrenalin junkie sitting in the chair as it is dragged down the frozen streets of Krasnoyarsk in central Russia's Krasnoyarsk Krai region, behind the Subaru Forester.

After spotting a car park where there were other young car drivers trying out drifting techniques, he and his friends decided to join in complete with armchair.

